{"tid":1593104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葵芳連儂隧道有習近平肖像被貼在地上","createTime":"2019-09-25T02:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T12:15:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61980a41cab9054243f452e9beb6959ad11b4c0d","tid":1593104,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190924/photo/bkn-20190924213511393-0924_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190925033434\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190924%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190924213511393-0924_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190925033434&h=90d55664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚(24日)多區都有遍地開花放映會，播放韓國電影《逆權公民》，當中包括葵芳港鐵站連儂隧道。放映會後，該隧道突然發現有大大小小約180張、印有國家主席習近平肖像的紙張貼在地上，有途人曾踐踏。<br />\n<br />\n另外，何文田港鐵站通往何文田邨天橋上的連儂牆，也有人在地上張貼習近平和立法會議員何君堯的肖像，但在深夜已經被全數撕去；網上亦流傳多名黑衣人在何文田連儂牆清理的片段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190924/photo/bkn-20190924213511393-0924_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190925033434\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190924%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190924213511393-0924_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190925033434&h=c8cbff4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190924/bkn-20190924213511393-0924_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2c4957f3354c1f1145bd0baaaa2b1c8a74534dd2","tid":1593104,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"84b48b62be29bb2038fb05d594a725b80ad785c6","tid":1593104,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:14:57